PrecisApproval of the re-appointment by the Minister of Public Works and Government Services of GLEN G. McDOUGALL, of Sydney, Nova Scotia, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Post Corporation to hold during pleasure for a term of three years, effective December 19, 1998.
